Just substitute the name of whichever ReTweetBot equipped account you want to use when you are posting.)</p>
<p>There are two basic ways of posting to a ReTweetBot equipped group.</p>

<ol>
	<li>
		<p>Using an @ reply. Simply start your Tweet with "@PredFans". Anyone can post to a group this way (if the administrator has the
		option enabled).</p>
